{"type":"answer","id":26663,"parentType":"question","parentId":6457,"uid":4516,"contents":"刚庆祝完圣诞，后面又是新年，中间再给个人庆生也太折腾了吧。不做啦睡大觉。<br>\n<br>\n哦对了给救世主过生日还是要的，但腊肉你又不是你靠边站，哦不，一边躺着去。再见<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/PgTVMhz.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PgTVMhz.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/PgTVMhz.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n—————修宪—————<br>\n这两天还有点闲，给老腊肉庆生也不是没时间<br>\n甚至，我还准备了一份有意义而且非常合适的礼物<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qA8Hyra.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qA8Hyra.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qA8Hyra.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-24","agreeCount":9,"discussionCount":0}